        <div class="p-10 max-w-6xl">

            <!-- ═══════════ SECTION: WELCOME ═══════════ -->
            <section id="s-welcome" class="section active">
                <div class="glass-warm rounded-3xl p-10 mb-6 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-saffron-300/5 blur-3xl drift"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl">
                        <div class="tag bg-saffron-300/10 text-saffron-200 border border-saffron-300/20 mb-6">A private demonstration</div>
                        <h2 class="serif text-5xl font-light text-cream-50 leading-[1.15] mb-6">For Dr. Veena — a quiet look at what could be, built around your practice.</h2>
                        <p class="text-ink-200 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light mb-6">This isn't a product pitch. It's a small demonstration of how the first layer of conversation with new clients could happen <em class="text-cream-50">before</em> it reaches you — in your voice, with your values, and without taking more of your time.</p>
                        <p class="text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">Scroll through at your own pace. Everything here is designed to be felt in under five minutes. There's a live chat you can try, a few small visualizations, and at the end, a simple suggestion for where we'd begin.</p>
