                        <p class="text-sm text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">Root causes before symptoms. Lifestyle before prescription. The person before the protocol.</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-ink-300 mt-4 italic">Every assistant response carries this tone — calm, grounded, never clinical-cold.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-300 font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-ink-300/20"></div><span>The four people who find you</span><div class="h-px flex-1 bg-ink-300/20"></div>
