                <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-6">
                    <div class="card glass rounded-2xl p-5 fade-up">
                        <div class="text-2xl mb-2">&#9792;</div>
                        <div class="serif text-xl text-cream-50 mb-2">Women's Health</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">Ovarian cysts, candidiasis, hormonal imbalance. Often underserved by conventional care.</div>
