                    <p class="serif text-xl text-cream-50 font-light italic leading-snug">You speak once. It helps many times. The mother awake at 2am with a sick child. The woman who felt dismissed by her GP. The curious seeker who hasn't yet dared to book. They hear you, even when you are resting.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 flex justify-end">
                    <button onclick="show('prototype')" class="bg-moss-600 hover:bg-moss-500 text-cream-50 px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">Where we'd begin &rarr;</button>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ═══════════ SECTION: PROTOTYPE ═══════════ -->
            <section id="s-prototype" class="section">
                <div class="glass-warm rounded-3xl p-8 mb-6">
                    <div class="tag bg-moss-400/10 text-moss-200 border border-moss-400/20 mb-4">Where we'd begin</div>
                    <h2 class="serif text-4xl font-light text-cream-50 leading-tight mb-4">One small thing, built well. Then everything else follows.</h2>
                    <p class="text-ink-200 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">We don't need a platform. We don't need a CRM overhaul. We need a single, gentle, visible proof that this works &mdash; in your voice, at your standard.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-6 items-center mb-8">
                    <div class="col-span-2 flex justify-center">
                        <div class="phone-frame p-1" style="width:260px;height:520px;">
                            <div class="w-full h-full rounded-[32px] bg-gradient-to-b from-ink-900 to-ink-950 p-4 overflow-hidden">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 pb-3 border-b border-white/5">
                                    <div class="lotus" style="width:28px;height:28px;font-size:11px;">S</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="text-[11px] text-cream-50 font-medium">Samayur</div>
                                        <div class="text-[8px] text-moss-300">online</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2">
                                    <div class="bubble-bot rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm p-2.5 max-w-[85%] text-[10px] text-cream-50 leading-snug">Welcome. I'm here to help you find out whether Samayur might be right for you.</div>
                                    <div class="bubble-user rounded-2xl rounded-tr-sm p-2.5 max-w-[80%] text-[10px] text-cream-50 leading-snug ml-auto">I've had bloating for years, nothing works.</div>
                                    <div class="bubble-bot rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm p-2.5 max-w-[85%] text-[10px] text-cream-50 leading-snug">That kind of persistent discomfort often points to something deeper. In Ayurveda, we call the digestive fire <em>Agni</em>...</div>
                                    <div class="bubble-bot rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm p-2.5 max-w-[85%] text-[10px] text-cream-50 leading-snug">May I ask a few gentle questions?</div>
                                    <div class="bubble-user rounded-2xl rounded-tr-sm p-2.5 max-w-[80%] text-[10px] text-cream-50 leading-snug ml-auto">Yes, please.</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-span-3 space-y-4">
                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
                            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-saffron-200 font-semibold mb-3">The first prototype</div>
                            <h3 class="serif text-3xl text-cream-50 mb-4">A WhatsApp assistant, trained on you.</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-ink-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">One link. Your existing number. No website changes. No new software for your clients to learn. They already use WhatsApp &mdash; so do you.</p>
                            <p class="text-sm text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">You share the link anywhere: on samayur.com, in your bio, in replies. When someone writes in, the assistant answers in your voice. Within days, you'll see the first real conversations happening &mdash; without you.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                            <div class="card glass rounded-xl p-4">
                                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-moss-300 mb-1">Timeline</div>
                                <div class="serif text-lg text-cream-50">Live in days</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-ink-300 mt-1">Not months</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card glass rounded-xl p-4">
                                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-moss-300 mb-1">Effort from you</div>
                                <div class="serif text-lg text-cream-50">One review</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-ink-300 mt-1">You approve the voice</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-300 font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-ink-300/20"></div><span>And then, in time</span><div class="h-px flex-1 bg-ink-300/20"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
                    <div class="card glass rounded-xl p-4">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-saffron-200 font-semibold mb-1">After the pilot</div>
                        <div class="serif text-lg text-cream-50 mb-1">Web widget</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">The assistant on samayur.com too &mdash; same voice, same intelligence.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card glass rounded-xl p-4">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-saffron-200 font-semibold mb-1">Month 2</div>
                        <div class="serif text-lg text-cream-50 mb-1">Dosha quiz</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">A beautiful, interactive lead-capture experience. Gentle entry point.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card glass rounded-xl p-4">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-saffron-200 font-semibold mb-1">Month 3</div>
                        <div class="serif text-lg text-cream-50 mb-1">Nurture flows</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">The gentle follow-up system, quietly running.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card glass rounded-xl p-4">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-saffron-200 font-semibold mb-1">Later</div>
                        <div class="serif text-lg text-cream-50 mb-1">Voice &amp; content</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">Your voice notes, traveling. Your knowledge, multiplied.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="glass-warm rounded-3xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-saffron-300/10 blur-3xl drift"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl">
                        <div class="tag bg-saffron-300/10 text-saffron-200 border border-saffron-300/20 mb-4">A closing note</div>
                        <p class="serif text-2xl text-cream-50 font-light leading-snug italic mb-6">"You built Samayur from real depth &mdash; from Gujarat, from years of study, from a kind of patience the modern world has mostly forgotten. What I'm offering is simply a way for that depth to be protected. So that the people who deserve your full presence get it. And the rest are still cared for, just earlier in the journey."</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-cream-50/10">
                            <div class="text-xs text-ink-300">Ready to see the first prototype built?</div>
                            <button class="bg-saffron-400 hover:bg-saffron-300 text-ink-900 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold transition">Let's begin &rarr;</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </div>
    </main>
</div>

<script>
    // ═════ NAVIGATION ═════
    const titles = {
        welcome: ['A Quiet Welcome', 'A demonstration prepared with care, for you'],
        understanding: ['Your Practice', 'What we understood before designing anything'],
        assistant: ['The Assistant', 'Try it as a new client would'],
        qualification: ['Smart Filtering', 'Who reaches you &mdash; and who doesn\'t yet'],
        time: ['Time Returned', 'The honest math of what this protects'],
        connection: ['Staying Connected', 'After the first conversation'],
        voice: ['Your Voice, Multiplied', 'Spoken once &mdash; traveling further'],
        prototype: ['Where We\'d Begin', 'The simplest first prototype']
    };
    function show(id) {
        document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));
        document.getElementById('s-'+id).classList.add('active');
        document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item').forEach(n => n.classList.remove('active'));
        document.querySelector('[data-s="'+id+'"]').classList.add('active');
        document.getElementById('stitle').innerHTML = titles[id][0];
        document.getElementById('ssub').innerHTML = titles[id][1];
        window.scrollTo({top:0, behavior:'smooth'});
    }

    // ═════ TIME CALCULATOR ═════
    function calcTime() {
        const inq = +document.getElementById('sInq').value;
        const min = +document.getElementById('sMin').value;
        document.getElementById('vInq').textContent = inq;
        document.getElementById('vMin').textContent = min;
        const dayH = (inq * min) / 60;
        const weekH = dayH * 7;
        const monthH = weekH * 4.33;
        document.getElementById('tDay').textContent = dayH.toFixed(1);
        document.getElementById('tWeek').textContent = weekH.toFixed(1);
        document.getElementById('tMonth').textContent = Math.round(monthH);
        const fullDays = Math.round(monthH / 8);
        const consultations = Math.round(monthH / 1);
        document.getElementById('equiv').innerHTML =
            '<span class="text-cream-50 font-medium">' + fullDays + ' full working days per month</span> &mdash; or <span class="text-cream-50 font-medium">' + consultations + ' additional deep consultations</span> with the patients who need you most.';
        document.getElementById('sInq').style.setProperty('--v', ((inq-1)/14*100)+'%');
        document.getElementById('sMin').style.setProperty('--v', ((min-5)/15*100)+'%');
    }

    // ═════ CHAT ═════
    const chatBody = document.getElementById('chatBody');
    const chipsEl = document.getElementById('chips');
    let chatState = { step: 0, segment: null, duration: null, tried: null, location: null };

    const initialChips = [
        { t: "I've had bloating and reflux for years", k: 'digestive' },
        { t: "I keep getting ovarian cysts", k: 'women' },
        { t: "My child has a recurring cough", k: 'parent' },
        { t: "I'm curious about Ayurveda", k: 'seeker' },
        { t: "How much does a consultation cost?", k: 'price' }
    ];

    function addBot(html, delay=700) {
        return new Promise(res => {
            const typing = document.createElement('div');
            typing.className = 'flex items-start gap-2 fade-up';
            typing.innerHTML = '<div class="lotus" style="width:28px;height:28px;font-size:11px;flex-shrink:0;">S</div><div class="bubble-bot rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm px-4 py-2.5"><div class="typing"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div></div>';
            chatBody.appendChild(typing);
            chatBody.scrollTop = chatBody.scrollHeight;
            setTimeout(() => {
                typing.querySelector('.bubble-bot').innerHTML = '<div class="text-sm text-cream-50 leading-relaxed">'+html+'</div>';
                chatBody.scrollTop = chatBody.scrollHeight;
                res();
            }, delay);
        });
    }
    function addUser(text) {
        const el = document.createElement('div');
        el.className = 'flex justify-end fade-up';
        el.innerHTML = '<div class="bubble-user rounded-2xl rounded-tr-sm px-4 py-2.5 max-w-[80%]"><div class="text-sm text-cream-50 leading-relaxed">'+text+'</div></div>';
        chatBody.appendChild(el);
        chatBody.scrollTop = chatBody.scrollHeight;
    }
    function setChips(list) {
        chipsEl.innerHTML = '';
        list.forEach(c => {
            const btn = document.createElement('button');
            btn.className = 'prompt-chip text-xs text-ink-200 bg-ink-900/60 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5';
            btn.textContent = c.t;
            btn.onclick = () => handleInput(c.t, c.k);
            chipsEl.appendChild(btn);
        });
    }

    async function handleInput(text, keyOverride=null) {
        addUser(text);
        const key = keyOverride || detectKey(text);
        chipsEl.innerHTML = '';

        if (chatState.step === 0) {
            chatState.segment = key;
            await routeSegment(key);
            chatState.step = 1;
            setChips([
                { t: 'About 3 years now', k: 'dur-long' },
                { t: 'A few months', k: 'dur-mid' },
                { t: 'Just started recently', k: 'dur-short' }
            ]);
        } else if (chatState.step === 1) {
            chatState.duration = key;
            await addBot("Thank you for sharing that. " + (key==='dur-long' ? "When something has been present for that long, it usually means the imbalance has layers to it &mdash; which is exactly where Ayurveda tends to be most useful." : key==='dur-mid' ? "That's actually a wonderful window &mdash; soon enough to address at the root, before the pattern becomes deeply set." : "Catching something early is a gift. Ayurveda is as much about prevention as it is about healing."));
            await addBot("May I ask &mdash; have you tried other approaches? Medical, dietary, or otherwise?", 900);
            chatState.step = 2;
            setChips([
                { t: "Yes, medications mainly", k: 'tried-meds' },
                { t: "Some diet changes", k: 'tried-diet' },
                { t: "Nothing yet", k: 'tried-none' }
            ]);
        } else if (chatState.step === 2) {
            chatState.tried = key;
            await addBot(key==='tried-meds' ? "Understood. Medications often manage symptoms beautifully but can leave the root untouched. That's usually what brings people to Dr. Veena." : key==='tried-diet' ? "It's thoughtful that you've already begun there &mdash; food is where Ayurveda always begins too. We simply take it deeper, into your individual constitution." : "No shame in that &mdash; in Ayurveda, the first step is always understanding, not acting. You're exactly where you should be.");
            await addBot("One last question &mdash; are you based in Portugal, or open to an online consultation?", 900);
            chatState.step = 3;
            setChips([
                { t: "I'm in Lisbon", k: 'loc-lisbon' },
                { t: "Algarve region", k: 'loc-algarve' },
                { t: "Online would be easier", k: 'loc-online' }
            ]);
        } else if (chatState.step === 3) {
            chatState.location = key;
            const locMap = { 'loc-lisbon': 'Lisbon (BeHaus)', 'loc-algarve': 'Portim&atilde;o or Almancil', 'loc-online': 'online' };
            await addBot("Perfect. Dr. Veena sees clients in " + locMap[key] + ", so that will work beautifully.");
            await addBot("Based on what you've shared, your situation sounds well-suited to the kind of work she does. A first consultation is a full medical evaluation &mdash; she uses Nadi Pariksha (pulse diagnosis) alongside a detailed conversation about your history, constitution, and current imbalances. It typically lasts about an hour.", 1100);
            await addBot("Would you like me to share the booking link? Or is there anything you'd like to ask first?", 900);
            chatState.step = 4;
            setChips([
                { t: "Yes, please send the booking link", k: 'book' },
                { t: "What does it cost?", k: 'price' },
                { t: "What should I prepare?", k: 'prepare' }
            ]);
            updateLeadCard();
        } else if (chatState.step === 4) {
            if (key === 'book' || text.toLowerCase().includes('book') || text.toLowerCase().includes('yes')) {
                await addBot("Wonderful. Here is the direct link: <span class='text-saffron-300 underline'>samayur.com/book</span>");
                await addBot("Before you go &mdash; may I send you a short guide on what to expect from your first Ayurvedic consultation? It helps you feel prepared and get the most from the time with Dr. Veena.", 1000);
                await addBot("You're in excellent hands. Looking forward to you meeting her.", 900);
                updateLeadCard(true);
                setChips([{ t: 'Restart the demo', k: 'reset' }]);
            } else if (key === 'price' || text.toLowerCase().includes('cost') || text.toLowerCase().includes('price')) {
                await addBot("The first consultation with Dr. Veena is &euro;120 and lasts approximately one hour. Follow-up consultations are &euro;80. Specific treatment programs &mdash; like Panchakarma &mdash; are quoted individually after the first session, because they are designed entirely around your needs.");
                setChips([{ t: "I'd like to book", k: 'book' }, { t: "Tell me more about treatments", k: 'treatments' }]);
            } else if (key === 'prepare' || text.toLowerCase().includes('prepare')) {
                await addBot("A few gentle things: note your typical daily meals, any medications you take, and how your digestion, sleep, and energy have been in the past weeks. Dr. Veena will guide you through the rest.");
                setChips([{ t: "I'd like to book", k: 'book' }]);
            } else {
                await addBot("I'll make sure Dr. Veena sees your message. Would you like the booking link in the meantime, so the slot is reserved for you?");
                setChips([{ t: "Yes, please", k: 'book' }]);
            }
        }
    }

    function detectKey(text) {
        const t = text.toLowerCase();
        if (t.match(/bloat|reflux|heartburn|digest|acid|stomach|gut|gas/)) return 'digestive';
        if (t.match(/cyst|candid|period|menstr|hormon|women|pcos|uti/)) return 'women';
        if (t.match(/child|kid|baby|son|daughter|fever|cough/)) return 'parent';
        if (t.match(/dosha|vata|pitta|kapha|philosoph|ayurveda|five element|curious|learn/)) return 'seeker';
        if (t.match(/cost|price|how much|pay|fee|euro/)) return 'price';
        if (t.match(/book|appointment|schedul/)) return 'book';
        return 'seeker';
    }

    async function routeSegment(key) {
        if (key === 'digestive') {
            await addBot("That kind of persistent discomfort &mdash; especially when nothing has helped long-term &mdash; often points to something deeper that hasn't been addressed.");
            await addBot("In Ayurveda, digestion is central to everything. We call the digestive fire <em>Agni</em>, and when it's disrupted, it shows up exactly the way you're describing.", 1000);
            await addBot("May I ask &mdash; how long has this been going on?", 900);
        } else if (key === 'women') {
            await addBot("I'm sorry you're dealing with this. Many women who come to Dr. Veena feel their concerns haven't been fully heard &mdash; and that the root cause is rarely addressed.");
            await addBot("In Ayurveda, these patterns are understood through the lens of accumulated heat, stress, and digestive imbalance &mdash; all treatable at the root.", 1000);
            await addBot("How long have you been dealing with this?", 900);
        } else if (key === 'parent') {
            await addBot("I can imagine how concerning that is. With children, Ayurveda has very gentle and time-tested approaches &mdash; especially for recurring issues that conventional treatment keeps returning to.");
            await addBot("Dr. Veena works with children carefully, always alongside your pediatrician, not in place of them.", 1000);
            await addBot("How long has this been recurring?", 900);
        } else if (key === 'seeker') {
            await addBot("That's a beautiful starting point. Ayurveda is a 5,000-year-old medical system &mdash; the word itself means <em>the science of life</em>. It begins not with symptoms, but with who you are.");
            await addBot("Dr. Veena trained at Gujarat Ayurved University in India, so the depth of her work is genuinely medical &mdash; not just lifestyle coaching.", 1000);
            await addBot("Is there a particular area of your health you'd like to understand better?", 900);
        } else if (key === 'price') {
            await addBot("A first consultation with Dr. Veena is &euro;120 and lasts approximately an hour. It's a full medical evaluation &mdash; she uses Nadi Pariksha (pulse diagnosis) alongside a detailed conversation about your history.");
            await addBot("Many people find that single session already gives them more clarity than years of searching.", 1000);
            await addBot("Is there a specific concern bringing you here?", 900);
        }
    }

    function updateLeadCard(booked=false) {
        const card = document.getElementById('leadCard');
        const dot = document.getElementById('leadDot');
        const status = document.getElementById('leadStatus');
        const content = document.getElementById('leadContent');
        card.classList.remove('opacity-40');
        dot.className = 'w-2 h-2 rounded-full ' + (booked ? 'bg-moss-300 pulse-dot' : 'bg-saffron-300 pulse-dot');
        status.textContent = booked ? 'Consultation booked' : 'Qualified lead — ready to review';

        const segMap = {
            digestive: 'Digestive &amp; Metabolic',
            women: "Women's Health",
            parent: 'Parent / Caregiver',
            seeker: 'Holistic Seeker',
            price: 'Information Seeker'
        };
        const durMap = { 'dur-long': '3+ years', 'dur-mid': 'Several months', 'dur-short': 'Recent onset' };
        const triedMap = { 'tried-meds': 'Medications (long-term)', 'tried-diet': 'Dietary changes', 'tried-none': 'Nothing yet' };
        const locMap = { 'loc-lisbon': 'Lisbon &mdash; BeHaus', 'loc-algarve': 'Algarve', 'loc-online': 'Online preferred' };

        content.innerHTML =
            '<div class="space-y-2.5 text-xs">' +
            '<div><div class="text-ink-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Segment</div><div class="text-cream-50 font-medium">' + (segMap[chatState.segment]||'&mdash;') + '</div></div>' +
            '<div><div class="text-ink-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Duration</div><div class="text-cream-50">' + (durMap[chatState.duration]||'&mdash;') + '</div></div>' +
            '<div><div class="text-ink-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Tried</div><div class="text-cream-50">' + (triedMap[chatState.tried]||'&mdash;') + '</div></div>' +
            '<div><div class="text-ink-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Location</div><div class="text-cream-50">' + (locMap[chatState.location]||'&mdash;') + '</div></div>' +
            '<div class="pt-2 mt-2 border-t border-white/5"><div class="text-ink-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Readiness</div><div class="text-moss-300 font-semibold">' + (booked ? 'Booked &mdash; prepare notes before session' : 'High &mdash; ready to book') + '</div></div>' +
            '</div>';
    }

    function sendUser() {
        const input = document.getElementById('chatInput');
        const val = input.value.trim();
        if (!val) return;
        input.value = '';
        handleInput(val);
    }
    document.getElementById('chatInput').addEventListener('keypress', e => {
        if (e.key === 'Enter') sendUser();
    });

    async function resetChat() {
        chatBody.innerHTML = '';
        chatState = { step: 0, segment: null, duration: null, tried: null, location: null };
        document.getElementById('leadCard').classList.add('opacity-40');
        document.getElementById('leadDot').className = 'w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-ink-400';
        document.getElementById('leadStatus').textContent = 'Awaiting conversation';
        document.getElementById('leadContent').innerHTML = '<div class="text-xs text-ink-400 italic">Start or complete the chat to see the summary the assistant would send you.</div>';
        await addBot("Welcome. I'm here to help you find out whether Samayur might be the right place for what you're going through.");
        await addBot("There's no rush. Tell me a little about what brought you today &mdash; a health concern, a question, or simply curiosity. I'll do my best to help.", 1100);
        setChips(initialChips);
    }

    // Initialize on load
    window.addEventListener('load', () => {
        calcTime();
        resetChat();
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>

